NAME
    Sah::Schemas::Color - Sah schemas related to color codes/names

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.014 of Sah::Schemas::Color (from Perl
    distribution Sah-Schemas-Color), released on 2021-07-19.

CONTRIBUTOR
    perlancar (on netbook-dell-xps13) <perlancar@gmail.com>

SAH SCHEMAS
    *   color::ansi16

        ANSI-16 color, either a number from 0-15 or color names like
        "black", "bold red", etc.

    *   color::ansi256

        ANSI-256 color, an integer number from 0-255.

    *   color::rgb24

        RGB 24-digit color, a hexdigit e.g. ffcc00.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
